title: Let's Play - Stainless Steel 6.4 - Medieval 2 Total War: Scotland #34 - The Grind Continues
description:
Welcome to part 34 of the Scottish campaign.  The battles against the Kingdom of  Aragon continue.  Their armies seem endless.  Will my forces have the heart to fight? enjoy :D
